<! [CDATA[
NutriAsia Logo
Nutri-Asia, Inc., formerly Southeast Asia Food, Inc., is a Philippine food company and the leading producer of condiment products in the Philippines. Among its best known brands are Datu Puti, Mang Tomas, UFC Catsup and Silver Swan. As of 2019, the company has of a total 116 distributors locally and international. NutriAsia was founded in 1991 as Enriton Natural Foods by Joselito Campos, the eldest son of industrialist José Yao Campos.
You can download theNutriAsialogo on full-version of the page.
